sequenceDiagram
    participant DataOwner
    participant DataGovernanceFramework
    participant GDPR
    participant PublicAdministrations
    participant CrossBorderSystem

    Note over DataOwner,CrossBorderSystem: Scenario: Data sharing and compliance under EU governance rules.
    DataOwner->>DataGovernanceFramework: Share Data
    DataGovernanceFramework->>GDPR: Check Compliance (e.g., privacy, consent)
    GDPR-->>DataGovernanceFramework: Compliance Status
    DataGovernanceFramework->>DataGovernanceFramework: Apply Data Governance Rules (e.g., DGA)
    DataGovernanceFramework->>SecureStorage: Store Data (Encrypted/Auditable)
    SecureStorage-->>DataGovernanceFramework: Confirm Secure Storage
    PublicAdministrations->>DataGovernanceFramework: Request Access & Validation
    DataGovernanceFramework-->>PublicAdministrations: Grant/Reject Access
    CrossBorderSystem->>DataGovernanceFramework: Verify Cross-Border Compliance
    DataGovernanceFramework-->>CrossBorderSystem: Compliance Certificate
